Reznick and Browne have dibs on cases this week.

92
00:02:04,790 --> 00:02:05,960
You make your picks?

93
00:02:05,980 --> 00:02:07,120
- Yes. - Definitely.

94
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:09,030
Is there karaoke?

95
00:02:09,490 --> 00:02:11,800
And now, our all-star lineup!

96
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:14,640
Playing center, out of Moose Jaw, Saskatchewan.

97
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:16,970
Spirit, stop it.

98
00:02:16,970 --> 00:02:18,450
They don't have time to fool around.

99
00:02:18,450 --> 00:02:19,590
I'm not fooling around.

100
